OL,3,CUp Close examines why families are
OL,4,Ccalling for reform of a crucial care
OL,5,Coption
OL,7,FBy Carol Jordan
OL,9,FWhen I was first put in touch with
OL,10,FTracey Henry in June of this year, I
OL,11,Fstruggled to get my head around the
OL,12,Fissue of direct payments.
OL,14,FTracey told me about her despair at
OL,15,Fwhy her carers under the system had
OL,16,Fbeen told that they could no longer
OL,17,Fcarry out health tasks.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/16
