OL,3,CUp Close examines why families are
OL,4,Ccalling for reform of a crucial care
OL,5,Coption
OL,7,FWhat ensued was an investigation into
OL,8,Fa part of the health and social care
OL,9,Fsystem which families say is riddled
OL,10,Fwith bureaucracy and difficult to
OL,11,Fnavigate but most importantly, is so
OL,12,Fessential for helping to meet the
OL,13,Fbasic human rights of its recipients
OL,14,Fand their families.
OL,16,FDirect payments can be applied for if
OL,17,Fyou are or care for someone with
OL,18,Fadditional or complex needs. The
OL,19,Fsystem works across both Children's
OL,20,Fand Adult's Services.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/16
