OL,3,CUp Close examines why families are
OL,4,Ccalling for reform of a crucial care
OL,5,Coption
OL,7,FIf you read the Direct Payment
OL,8,Flegislation it states that the
OL,9,Fpayments should be used for social
OL,10,Fcare needs.
OL,12,FBut with someone with complex needs,
OL,13,Fthe boundaries between what
OL,14,Fconstitutes health or medical needs
OL,15,Fand social needs blur.
OL,17,FIf you need hourly medication or feeds
OL,18,Fthrough a peg, then anyone who cares
OL,19,Ffor you needs to be able to manage
OL,20,Fthat process so the basic human needs
OL,21,Fof nutrition and medication can be met.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
