OL,7,FAnd for Ellie, any opportunity she had
OL,8,Fto go out without her parent like any
OL,9,Fother young woman was also gone.
OL,11,FWhen I approached the Northern Trust,
OL,12,Fin a statement from last June, it told
OL,13,Fme that it was looking at the
OL,14,Flegislation around Direct Payments.
OL,16,FAnd it's that legislation which Tracey
OL,17,Fwants changed. She has started a
OL,18,Fpetition which has garnered almost
OL,19,F20,000 signatures to date.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
