OL,7,FShe argues it's the only way that
OL,8,Fconfusion around Direct Payments and
OL,9,Fwho is entitled to what can be cleared
OL,10,Fup. It's a call which is supported by
OL,11,Fexperts.
OL,13,FDeena Nimick from the Centre For
OL,14,FIndependent Living which helps people
OL,15,Fnavigate the Direct Payment system
OL,16,Fagrees that the law is unclear.
