OL,7,FShe says that from late last year she
OL,8,Fhas seen an update in calls from
OL,9,Fpeople from across Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fwho also claim their carers have been
OL,11,Fstopped from undertaking health care
OL,12,Ftasks.
OL,14,FNuala Toman from Disability Action
OL,15,Fagrees. She argues that the system is
OL,16,Fconfusing and there needs to be a
OL,17,Flevel playing field.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
