OL,7,FCaroline Wheeler is mum to Lee. Lee is
OL,8,F40 years old and is the only person to
OL,9,Flive with Double/Triple Mosaic
OL,10,FSyndrome.
OL,12,FHe's epileptic, diabetic, has learning
OL,13,Fdifficulties amongst other conditions
OL,14,Fbut remarkably, he lives independently
OL,15,Fsupported by a 24/7 care package
OL,16,Fincluding Caroline, who is paid as one
OL,17,Fof his carers under Direct Payments.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/16
