OL,7,FWhen asked about Direct Payment
OL,8,Flegislation, the Department of Health
OL,9,Fsaid that it was working with trusts
OL,10,Fto address the issues.
OL,12,FIt said it has started a Start and
OL,13,FFinish force to look at the system and
OL,14,Fapologises for any disruption in
OL,15,Fservices. Crucially, it said it had
OL,16,Falso received its own legal advice.
OL,18,FThe Trusts run the Direct Payments
OL,19,Fsystem. Their responses show the
OL,20,Fdisparity between the trusts' approach.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/16
