OL,7,FWhen approached about Tracey's case,
OL,8,Fthe Northern Trust told Up Close that
OL,9,Fit had received legal guidance in May
OL,10,F2022 which led it to conclude that
OL,11,Fcarers under Direct Payments cannot
OL,12,Fundertake healthcare or nursing tasks.
OL,14,FHowever, Tracey wasn't informed about
OL,15,Fchanges to her package until April of
OL,16,Fthis year, almost two years later.
OL,18,FWhen approached by Up Close the other
OL,19,Ffour HSC Trusts said:
OL,21,FSouth Eastern Health Trust
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
