OL,7,FThe South Eastern Trust say their
OL,8,Fpolicy has not changed, however some
OL,9,Fdirect payment carers may carry out
OL,10,Ftasks which could be described as
OL,11,Fnursing or healthcare in which case
OL,12,Fappropriate training is provided.
OL,14,FBelfast Trust
OL,16,FThe Belfast Trust also say their
OL,17,Fpolicy on direct payment carers hasn't
OL,18,Fchanged and that on occasion some
OL,19,Fcarers may carry out nursing and
OL,20,Fhealthcare tasks for which they would
OL,21,Fprovide appropriate training.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
