OL,7,FThe Southern Trust's position remains
OL,8,Fthat Direct Payments should only be
OL,9,Fused for social care tasks. A
OL,10,Fsituation may arise, of a carer who
OL,11,Fhas decided to train up their personal
OL,12,Fassistant to manage specific
OL,13,Fhealthcare tasks. When this situation
OL,14,Femerges, a multi-disciplinary approach
OL,15,Fwill be taken in partnership with the
OL,16,Findividual and their Parent/Carer to
OL,17,Freplace this with Trust arranged
OL,18,Fsupport.
