OL,7,FAs for the families at the centre of
OL,8,Fthis, there are no easy answers. They
OL,9,Fneed Direct Payment carers to help
OL,10,Fprovide the best level of care for
OL,11,Ftheir loved ones.
OL,13,FAnd by doing that they save the health
OL,14,Fsystem and all tax-payers the cost of
OL,15,Fresidential care...
OL,17,FThey continue to call for reform...
OL,18,FThey continue to fight for care.
